Note on data licensing:

The khipu data bundled within the HTML files of this repository was derived
from the Open Khipu Repository / Harvard Khipu Database Project
(http://khipukamayuq.fas.harvard.edu/), which is maintained by Harvard
University. Use of that data may be subject to terms set by Harvard and the
project's principal investigators (Gary Urton, Carrie Brezine, et al.).
Users wishing to redistribute or build upon the embedded data should consult
the original source for its licensing terms.

The Quechua wordlist and the Quechua gematria system embedded in this tool
are original work by Dogan Balban (2026), released under the MIT license
above.
